    "explanation": "Step 1: This is a telescoping series: each term cancels the next.\nStep 2: (1вИТвИЪ2)+(вИЪ2вИТвИЪ3)+...+(вИЪ15вИТвИЪ16) вАФ all middle terms cancel.\nStep 3: What remains: 1 вИТ вИЪ16 = 1 вИТ 4 = вИТ3.\nFinal Answer: -3"
