    "explanation": "Step 1: Weighted avg: 5200.0√Ч(male%) + 4200.0√Ч(female%) = 5000.0. Let female% = p.\nStep 2: 5200.0√Ч(1вИТp/100) + 4200.0√Ч(p/100) = 5000.0.\nStep 3: (5200.0вИТ4200.0)√Ч(1вИТp/100) = 5000.0вИТ4200.0 вЖТ p = (5200.0вИТ5000.0)/(5200.0вИТ4200.0)√Ч100 = 20%.\nFinal Answer: 20%"
  },
